        <bioghist id="ref5">
            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Ansel Hayes Van Buren (1846-1910) married Idelle Newell on November 11, 1884. Ansel was an acomplished musician and salesman with various piano houses in Brooklyn. He and Idelle lived in the Brooklyn neighborhood of Flatbush.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref2">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Bond of Ansel and Idelle Van Buren of $21,000 to Henry Lankenau. Signed by a Kings County notary public and dated 1891.</p>
        </scopecontent>
